msgctxt "56_Tanimura"
msgid "Hey, what's up, Chief?"
msgstr "Ey, ¿qué pasa, jefe?"

msgctxt "68_Hisai"
msgid "Is that all you have to say? You went to a mahjong parlor during your patrol yesterday. That's \"what's up\"!"
msgstr "¿Es eso todo lo que tienes que decir? Fuiste a un salón de mahjong durante tu patrulla de ayer. ¡Eso es \"lo qué pasa\"!"

msgctxt "80_Tanimura"
msgid "Hmm... I did?"
msgstr "Uf... ¿Lo hice?"

msgctxt "92_Hisai"
msgid "This isn't a joke! Please, don't gamble while you're on duty. I shouldn't have to remind you."
msgstr "¡Esto no es una broma! Por favor, no juegues mientras estás de servicio. No debería tener que recordártelo."

msgctxt "104_Tanimura"
msgid "Okay, all right..."
msgstr "Oh, está bien..."

msgctxt "116_Hisai"
msgid "Look, someone called in saying you took them for tens of thousands of yen. What do I say to that?"
msgstr "Escucha, alguien llamó diciendo que les quitaste una fortuna. ¿Qué quieres que diga?"

msgctxt "128_Tanimura"
msgid "Who'd you say called that in?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140_Hisai"
msgid "I didn't! I can only imagine what you'd do to the poor fellow if I did!"
msgstr "¡No lo hice! ¡Solo imagino lo que le harías al pobre tipo si lo hubiera hecho!"

msgctxt "152_Tanimura"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "164_Hisai"
msgid "Anyway, think of the position you're putting me in here."
msgstr "De todos modos, piensa en la posición en la que me estás poniendo aquí."

msgctxt "176_Hisai"
msgid "What would I say to your father, letting you run amok like this?"
msgstr "¿Qué le diré a tu padre, dejándote hacer lo que quieras?"

msgctxt "188_Hisai"
msgid "I should mention I risked my neck pulling you into Community Safety. Have you ever considered that?"
msgstr "Debería mencionarte que arriesgué el cuello metiéndote en Seguridad Comunitaria. ¿Lo has considerado alguna vez?"

msgctxt "200_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, you're right... Sorry."
msgstr "Sí, tienes razón... Lo siento."

msgctxt "212_Hisai"
msgid "At least make an effort to stay on track, all right?"
msgstr "Solo intenta mantener el rumbo, ¿vale?"

